title: EA Sports College Football Is Back - Kinda Funny Games Daily 02.02.21
description:
Greg and Gary Whitta have a show CRAMMED with news -- #EASportsCollegeFootball is back, #MassEffectLegendaryEdition has a date, and #Stadia stopped internal development!

00:00:00 - Start
00:05:57 - Housekeeping
A HUGE day of content!
Youtube.com/kindafunnygames has a new PSILY and a Mass Effect: Legendary Preview from Andy and Parris.
Patreon.com/kindafunnygames will have the Gamescast today as we talk about Xbox Game Pass
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: GrahamOfLegend, David Meintel, Trent Berrie, Black Jack, Luiz Aguiar (@8bitLuiz), James Davis (@JamesDavisMakes), &The Nano Biologist
The Roper Report   -
00:08:11 - EA Sports College Football is Back!
00:28:30 - Mass Effect Legendary Edition Details
00:45:30 -  Ad
00:48:05 - Stadia Kills Internal Development, Stephen Totillo @ Kotaku
01:04:25 - Out today
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Greg and Gary
